abh Sinha]]\n|-\n|[[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 10)|10]]\n|2016\u201317\n|Bigg Boss India Yeh Tumhara hi Ghar hai\n|16 October 2016\n|28 January 2017\n|18\n|style=\"background:cyan;|Manveer Gurjar\n|style=\"background:pink;\" |[[Gurbani Judge|Bani J]]\n|-\n|[[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 11)|11]]\n|2017\u201318\n|Bigg Boss Padosi Bajayege Barah\n|1 October 2017\n|14 January 2018\n|106\n|19\n|style=\"background:pink;\" |[[Shilpa Shinde]]\n|style=\"background:pink;\" |[[Hina Khan]]\n|-\n|[[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 12)|12]]\n|2018\n|Bigg Boss Barah\n|16 September 2018\n|30 December 2018\n|105\n|20\n|style=\"background:pink;\"|[[Dipika Kakar]]\n|style=\"background:cyan;\"|[[S. Sreesanth]]\n|-\n|[[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 13)|13]]\n|2019\u201320\n|Bigg Boss Tedah: Celebrity Express\n| rowspan=\"1\" | [[Goregaon]]\n|29 September 2019\n|15 February 2020\n|140\n|22\n|style=\"background:cyan;\"|[[Sidharth Shukla]]\n|style=\"background:cyan;\"|Asim Riaz\n|-\n| colspan=\"17\" |\n|-\n|rowspan=\"7\" style=\"background:#fff2a5;\" |[[Kannada]]\n| rowspan=\"7\" |''[[Bigg Boss Kannada|Bigg Boss<br>Kannada]]''\n|[[Bigg Boss Kannada 1|1]]\n|2013\n|Bigg Boss\n|[[ETV Kannada]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |N/A\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Lonavla|Lonavala]]\n|24 March 2013\n|30 June 2013\n| rowspan=\"3\" |98\n| rowspan=\"2\" |15\n| rowspan=\"7\" |{{INRConvert|50|l}}\n| rowspan=\"7\" |[[Sudeep]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Amit Bhargav]]\n| style=\"background:cyan;\" |[[Vijay Raghavendra]]\n| style=\"background:cyan;\" |[[Arun Sagar]]\n|-\n|[[Bigg Boss Kannada 2|2]]\n|2014\n|Bigg Boss Season 2\n|[[Star Suvarna]]\n|29 June 2014\n|5 October 2014\n|style=\"background:cyan;\" |[[Akul Balaji]]\n|style=\"background:cyan;\" |[[Srujan Lokesh]]\n|-\n|[[Bigg Boss Kannada 3|3]]\n|2015\u201316\n|Bigg Boss\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Colors Kannada|Colors<br>Kannada]]\n| rowspan=\"5\" |[[Voot]]\n| rowspan=\"5\" |[[Bangalore|Bengaluru]]\n|25 October 2015\n|31 January 2016\n| rowspan=\"2\" |18\n| rowspan=\"5\" |Srinivas Prasad\n|style=\"background:p